These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, scooter, roller
4 different games are played: poker, domino, whist, go
House: farmhouse, victorian, wooden, craftsman
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the victorian house##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the farmhouse house is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the victorian house is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person playing whist is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the owner of the horse is the person playing domino##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Transport         | roller    | scooter   | tram | helicopter      |
| Game   | domino       | poker | whist     | go    |
| House   | craftsman | victorian         | farmhouse  | wooden    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

