.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, russian, chinese
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, february, march
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, hiking, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the russian is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | colombian | mexican   | russian   | chinese           |
| Birthday   | november  | march     | february    | september         |
| Hobby           | singing         | reading | hiking     | sudoku        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

