.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving, magic-tricks, baking
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, tea, juice
City: rome, london, boston, liverpool
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Hobby   | baking     | magic-tricks      | skydiving | woodworking      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | tea  | juice |
| City     | boston       | rome         | liverpool   | london        |

