.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
City: liverpool, new-york, berlin, london
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, ritmeester, blend
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
House: cape-cod, craftsman, tower, wooden
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 3. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the wooden house is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| City          | berlin     | liverpool   | london | new-york |
| Cigar   | cain | ritmeester | bolivar   | blend       |
| Pet           | goat       | cat      | snake     | guinea-pig |
| House     | cape-cod    | tower     | wooden     | craftsman     |

