There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, milk, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, lizard, snake
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person eating potato##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who likes black##1
14. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | kale       | mango     | potato     | pumpkin  |
| Color         | azure  | black | apricot | brown  |
| Sport           | skiing | badminton    | swimming    | ice-hockey |
