.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, gardening, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, doctor, coach, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, cola, lemonade
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, chess, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the doctor is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the police-officer is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
10. the person playing chess is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the software-developer##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing   | gardening | skydiving    | card-games  |
| Job   | police-officer    | software-developer | coach      | doctor |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite | lemonade         | coffee  |
| Game         | scrabble  | chess     | monopoly | whist     |
| Transport     | bike      | van       | ship         | car         |

