 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking water is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking water##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
