The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, hiking, reading
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, light-blue, blood-red, lilac
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the doctor is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the accountant is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
 7. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the doctor is the fan of r&b##1
10. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the paramedic is the fan of indie##1
12. the writer is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | accountant | writer | doctor     | paramedic |
| Sport   | volleyball    | badminton   | soccer | baseball   |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | house  | r&b        | indie     |
