.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water
House: ranch-style, townhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, photographer, security-guard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, bongani, chaman
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, red, mauve, white
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the firefighter##1
 2. the ranch-style house is the firefighter##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 5. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the person who likes coral is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes red##1
10. the person drinking water is the swisher-smoker##1
11. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the townhouse house##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| House       | cape-cod    | gothic-revival        | ranch-style  | townhouse      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Cigar         | baccarat | chaman          | swisher         | bongani      |
| Color   | red     | coral     | mauve       | white          |

