 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the colombian is the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the brazilian##1
10. the person eating grapes is the chinese##1
11. the chinese is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the chinese is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

